Class UpperExpressionStateObject

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StateObject

    public class UpperExpressionStateObject
extends AbstractSingleEncapsulatedExpressionStateObject
    The UPPER function converts a string to upper case and it returns a string.
    BNF: expression ::= UPPER(string_primary)

    Version:
    2.4
    See Also:
    UpperExpression
    Author:
    Pascal Filion
    Since:
    2.4
